quran[16{c,v,t}:
15,16,aur hum hi ne aasman mein burj banaye aur dekhnay walon ke liye uss ko saja diya
15,17,aur har shetan راندہٴ dargaah se ussay mehfooz kar diya
15,18,haan agar koi chori se sunna chahay to chamakta howa angara is ke peechay lpkta hai
15,19,aur zameen ko bhi hum hi ne phelaya aur is par pahar ( bana kar ) rakh diye aur is mein har aik sanjeeda cheez ugai
15,20,aur hum hi ne tumahray liye aur un logon ke liye jin ko tum rozi nahi dete is mein muaash ke samaan peda kiye
15,21,aur hamaray haan har cheez ke khazanay hain aur hum un ko بمقدار munhasib utaartay rehtay hain
15,22,aur hum hi hawae chillate hain ( jo baadalon ke pani se ) bhari hui hoti hain aur hum hi aasman se meen barastee hain aur hum hi tum ko is ka pani pilate hain aur tum to is ka خرانہ nahi rakhtay
15,23,aur hum hi hayaat bkhshte aur hum hi mout dete hain. aur hum sab ke waris ( maalik ) hain
15,24,aur jo log tum mein pehlay guzar chuke hain hum ko maloom hain aur jo peechay anay walay hain woh bhi hum ko maloom hain
15,25,aur tumhara perwar-digaar ( qayamat ke din ) un sab ko jama kere ga woh bara Dana ( aur ) khabardaar hai
15,26,aur hum ne ensaan ko khankhnate sarray hue gaaray se pedakiya hai
15,27,aur junoo ko is se bhi pehlay be dhowen ki aag se pedakiya tha
15,28,aur jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne firshton se farmaya ke mein khankhnate srhe hue gaaray se aik bashar bananay wala hon
15,29,jab is ko ( soorat ainsaniya mein ) durust kar lon aur is mein apni ( be baha cheez yani ) rooh phoonk dun to is ke agay sjday mein gir parna
15,30,to farishtay to sab ke sab sjday mein gir parre
15,31,magar shetan ke is ne sajda karne walon ke sath honay se inkaar kar diya
